# Build artifacts. The top-level .gitignore already covers __pycache__,
# .DS_Store, *.dSYM, etc.; these are the extensionless C binaries the Hoare
# Makefile builds next to their sources. (Compiled JVM example classes are
# ignored by vm-theory/code/jvm/.gitignore.)
